---
import { C, FONT } from "../infographicTokens";
---

<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 720 320" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
  <title>New install vs straight replacement cost</title>
  <desc>Two cards comparing a new central AC install that adds ductwork against a like-for-like replacement that reuses existing ducts, showing the replacement is cheaper.</desc>

  <text x="360" y="30" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="16" font-weight="700">New install vs straight replacement</text>

  <!-- Card 1: New install (with ductwork) -->
  <rect x="40" y="56" width="300" height="216" rx="14" fill={C.orangeLight} stroke={C.orange} stroke-width="1.5" />
  <text x="190" y="88" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="14" font-weight="800">New install (with ductwork)</text>
  <text x="190" y="132" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.orange} font-family={FONT} font-size="28" font-weight="800">$7,000&#8211;$13,000+</text>
  <text x="190" y="154" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.muted} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="600">first-time central air</text>

  <text x="62" y="190" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11.5" font-weight="700">+ New duct runs &amp; returns</text>
  <text x="62" y="214" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11.5" font-weight="700">+ New line set &amp; electrical</text>
  <text x="62" y="238" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11.5" font-weight="700">+ Air handler / coil &amp; condenser</text>
  <text x="62" y="262" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11.5" font-weight="700">+ More labor, permits, drywall</text>

  <!-- Card 2: Like-for-like replacement -->
  <rect x="380" y="56" width="300" height="216" rx="14" fill={C.primaryLight} stroke={C.primary} stroke-width="1.5" />
  <text x="530" y="88" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="14" font-weight="800">Replacement (reuse ducts)</text>
  <text x="530" y="132" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.primary} font-family={FONT} font-size="28" font-weight="800">$3,800&#8211;$8,000</text>
  <text x="530" y="154" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.muted} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="600">swap an existing system</text>

  <text x="402" y="190" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11.5" font-weight="700">+ Existing ducts kept</text>
  <text x="402" y="214" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11.5" font-weight="700">+ Often reuse line set</text>
  <text x="402" y="238" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11.5" font-weight="700">+ Condenser + coil only</text>
  <text x="402" y="262" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="11.5" font-weight="700">+ Less labor, faster job</text>

  <text x="360" y="300" text-anchor="middle" fill={C.muted} font-family={FONT} font-size="11">Adding ducts is the single biggest jump; a like-for-like swap is the cheaper path when ducts are sound.</text>
</svg>
